                    <title>Example: Partial Sums</title>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            <me>
                                \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac{1}{2^{n-1}} = 
                            </me>
                            
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                    <solution>
                        <p>
                            To get an idea if this series converges or diverges, we can compute several partial sums:
