                                        <m>S_4 = \frac{15}{8}</m>
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            Using technology, we can guess that the partial sums converge to <m>2</m>.
                        </p>
                    </solution>
                    
                </exercise>
            </page>

